Gentoo ebuild.

You must have a working portage overlay.

create $YOUR_OVERLAY/app-editors/yzis directory.
copy the ebuild to this directory using yzis-0.1_preYYYYMMDD.ebuild format (to get the latest daily tarball).
run /usr/sbin/ebuild $YOUR_OVERLAY/app-editors/yzis/yzis-0.1_preYYYYMMDD.ebuild digest
then emerge yzis.

3 use flags :
- kde : enable kyzis
- ncurses : enable nyzis
- pslib : add pslib dependencie

